

### curl request
/*
curl -X POST "http://localhost:8082/api/v1/security/admin/ip/blacklist/192.168.1.100?reason=Testing&durationMinutes=60" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer ADMIN_TOKEN"

# Try accessing from blacklisted IP
curl -X GET http://localhost:8082/api/v1/users/profile \
  -H "X-Forwarded-For: 192.168.1.100"
*/
GET http://localhost:8082/api/v1/users/profile
Authorization: Bearer ADMIN_TOKEN
X-Forwarded-For: 192.168.1.100

